                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8515" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0251</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1247 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“刻”尽其责：一刻公益的“志愿反哺”履责成效评估</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Fulfilling Responsibility to the Fullest: Evaluating the Effectiveness of &quot;voluntary feeding&quot; in BYPWF</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">白旻，赵佳琦，王蓉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京一刻公益基金会</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公共管理和社会组织</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">一刻公益；非营利组织；社会责任；“APC”评估理论；2024百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">BYPWF; Nonprofit Organization; Social Responsibility; &quot;APC&quot; Evaluation Theory</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了北京一刻公益基金会作为以“志愿反哺”模式为特色的非营利组织，面对我国《“十四五”社会组织发展规划》对社会组织高质量发展提出的新要求，迅速明晰履责方向、逐步规划履责层次、落实推进履责行动。一刻公益遵循“组织－项目－活动”的履责路径，从多维度加强组织自身建设，进而在自身组织结构合理、治理合规的前提下，结合不同地区、街道的资源与特征打造有特色的示范项目，最后通过项目落地后具体活动的筹划与组织，将履责行动贯彻到最小单元的履责实践，以期引导学生掌握非营利组织的社会责任内涵、履责必要性、非营利组织“APC”评估理论及可持续发展策略。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study describes how Beijing Yike Public Welfare Foundation (BYPWF), a non-profit organization characterized by its &quot;volunteer reciprocation&quot; model, swiftly clarified its responsibility direction, gradually planned responsibility levels, and implemented responsibility actions in response to the new requirements for high-quality development of social organizations outlined in China&#39;s 14th Five-Year Plan for Social Organization Development. Yike Public Welfare follows a &quot;Organization-Project-Activity&quot; path for fulfilling its responsibilities. It strengthens its organizational development from multiple dimensions, builds well-structured and compliant governance, and creates distinctive demonstration projects by leveraging resources and characteristics of different regions and streets. Finally, through planning and organizing specific activities for the implemented projects, it integrates responsibility actions into the smallest unit of practice. The aim is to guide students in understanding the social responsibility of non-profit organizations, the necessity of fulfilling these responsibilities, the &quot;APC&quot; evaluation theory for non-profits, and sustainable development strategies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">非营利组织的社会责任；非营利组织履责必要性；“APC”评估理论；非营利组织的可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
